<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>EXECUTION SYSTEM</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Bebas+Neue&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:#0a0a0a;--surface:#111;--surface2:#1a1a1a;--border:#2a2a2a;
    --accent:#e8ff00;--accent2:#ff4d00;--accent3:#00ffcc;--text:#f0f0f0;--muted:#666;--danger:#ff3333;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;}
  nav{display:flex;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:100;}
  .tab{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;padding:16px 20px;cursor:pointer;border-right:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);transition:all .2s;text-transform:uppercase;background:transparent;user-select:none;}
  .tab:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--surface);}
  .tab.active{color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface);border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent);}
  .logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:22px;padding:14px 28px;letter-spacing:4px;margin-left:auto;color:var(--accent);border-left:1px solid var(--border);}
  .page{display:none;padding:40px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;}
  .page.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn .25s ease;}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  .page-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:72px;letter-spacing:6px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .page-sub{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:48px;}
  h3{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px;}
  .card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:28px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;}
  .grid3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px;}
  textarea,input[type="text"],select{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-size:14px;padding:12px 16px;width:100%;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;resize:none;}
  textarea:focus,input:focus,select:focus{border-color:var(--accent);}
  select option{background:var(--surface2);}
  textarea.brain-dump{min-height:180px;line-height:1.8;}
  .btn{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px 28px;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all .2s;}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#000;}.btn-primary:hover{background:#fff;}
  .btn-secondary{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);}.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
  .btn-danger{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--danger);color:var(--danger);}.btn-danger:hover{background:var(--danger);color:#fff;}
  .btn-sm{padding:8px 16px;font-size:10px;}.btn-xs{padding:5px 10px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;}

  .dump-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:6px;background:var(--surface);}
  .dump-text{font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .dump-actions{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

  .big3-item{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--accent);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .big3-item.all-done{border-left-color:var(--accent3);opacity:.6;}
  .big3-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;}
  .big3-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:48px;color:var(--accent);line-height:1;min-width:40px;}
  .big3-item.all-done .big3-num{color:var(--accent3);}
  .big3-content{flex:1;}
  .big3-label{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;}
  .big3-text{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .big3-actions{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;align-items:flex-end;}

  .subtask-hint{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:#aaa;letter-spacing:1px;margin:6px 0 12px;padding:9px 12px;border-left:2px solid var(--accent);background:#0f1400;line-height:1.8;}
  .subtask-list{margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
  .subtask-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1c1c1c;}
  .subtask-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .sub-check{width:20px;height:20px;border:2px solid var(--border);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .15s;}
  .sub-check:hover{border-color:var(--accent3);}
  .sub-check.done{border-color:var(--accent3);background:var(--accent3);}
  .sub-check.done::after{content:'✓';color:#000;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;}
  .sub-text{flex:1;font-size:13px;}
  .sub-text.done{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--muted);}
  .subtask-add{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;}
  .subtask-add input{font-size:12px;padding:8px 12px;}
  .progress-bar{height:3px;background:var(--surface2);margin-top:8px;overflow:hidden;}
  .progress-fill{height:100%;background:var(--accent);transition:width .4s ease;}
  .progress-text{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px;}

  .filter-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .filter-btn{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:6px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .15s;}
  .filter-btn.active{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
  .backlog-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:6px;background:var(--surface);transition:background .15s;}
  .backlog-item:hover{background:var(--surface2);}
  .cat-badge{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;padding:2px 8px;border:1px solid;text-transform:uppercase;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;letter-spacing:1px;}

  .time-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;gap:4px;max-height:600px;overflow-y:auto;}
  .time-label{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);padding:6px 8px;text-align:right;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;letter-spacing:1px;}
  .time-block{min-height:48px;border:1px solid var(--border);padding:8px 12px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--surface);}
  .time-block:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .time-block.deep{background:#1a1f00;border-color:#3a4a00;}
  .time-block.admin{background:#0d1a1a;border-color:#0a3333;}
  .time-block.personal{background:#1a0d1a;border-color:#330033;}
  .time-block.buffer{background:#1a1000;border-color:#332000;}
  .time-block.done-block{opacity:.4;text-decoration:line-through;}
  .block-tag{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 6px;border:1px solid;}
  .tag-deep{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);}
  .tag-admin{color:var(--accent3);border-color:var(--accent3);}
  .tag-personal{color:#cc88ff;border-color:#cc88ff;}
  .tag-buffer{color:var(--accent2);border-color:var(--accent2);}

  .modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.88);z-index:1000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .modal-overlay.open{display:flex;}
  .modal{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px;width:520px;max-width:95vw;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto;}
  .modal h2{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:36px;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:24px;color:var(--accent);}
  .form-row{margin-bottom:16px;}
  .form-label{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;display:block;}
  .modal-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:24px;}
  .stat-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:24px;text-align:center;}
  .stat-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:56px;letter-spacing:2px;line-height:1;color:var(--accent);}
  .stat-label{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:8px;}
  .header-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:24px;}
  .divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:32px 0;}
  .check-btn{width:28px;height:28px;border:2px solid var(--border);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s;flex-shrink:0;}
  .check-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent3);}
  .check-btn.checked{border-color:var(--accent3);background:var(--accent3);}
  .check-btn.checked::after{content:'✓';color:#000;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;}
  .focus-banner{background:var(--accent);color:#000;padding:14px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .focus-timer{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:28px;letter-spacing:3px;}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px;}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg);}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);}
  .import-tab{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:8px 0;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);flex:1;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .15s;}
  .import-tab.active{background:var(--accent);color:#000;border-color:var(--accent);}

  /* DATE BAR */
  .date-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);position:sticky;top:49px;z-index:99;}
  .date-nav-btn{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:16px;padding:10px 20px;cursor:pointer;border:none;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);transition:all .15s;user-select:none;}
  .date-nav-btn:hover{color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface2);}
  .date-nav-btn:last-child{border-right:none;border-left:1px solid var(--border);}
  .date-display{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:3px;padding:10px 28px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text);border:none;background:transparent;transition:all .15s;text-transform:uppercase;min-width:280px;text-align:center;}
  .date-display:hover{color:var(--accent);}
  .date-display.future{color:var(--accent3);}
  .date-display.past{color:var(--muted);}
  .not-today-banner{background:var(--surface2);border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent3);padding:10px 40px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--accent3);display:none;}
  .not-today-banner.future{border-color:var(--accent3);color:var(--accent3);}
  .not-today-banner.past{border-color:var(--muted);color:var(--muted);}
  /* CUSTOM CALENDAR POPUP */
  #calPopup{display:none;position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 4px);left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:20px;z-index:500;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.8);min-width:300px;}
  .cal-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .cal-month-label{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--accent);}
  .cal-nav{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:14px;padding:4px 12px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);transition:all .15s;}
  .cal-nav:hover{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);}
  .cal-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:3px;}
  .cal-day-label{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;text-align:center;color:var(--muted);padding:4px 0;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .cal-day-label:first-child{color:#ff6666;}
  .cal-day-label:last-child{color:#6699ff;}
  .cal-cell{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;text-align:center;padding:7px 4px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;transition:all .15s;position:relative;}
  .cal-cell:hover:not(.empty){border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
  .cal-cell.empty{cursor:default;pointer-events:none;}
  .cal-cell.today-cell{border-color:var(--accent)!important;color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;}
  .cal-cell.selected-cell{background:var(--accent);color:#000!important;font-weight:700;border-color:var(--accent)!important;}
  .cal-cell.has-data::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:2px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent3);}
  .cal-cell.selected-cell.has-data::after{background:#000;}
  .cal-cell.sun{color:#ff6666;}
  .cal-cell.sat{color:#6699ff;}
  .cal-cell.other-month{opacity:.3;}
  .cal-footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
  .cal-today-btn{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;padding:6px 14px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--accent);background:transparent;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .15s;}
  .cal-today-btn:hover{background:var(--accent);color:#000;}
  .cal-legend{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
  .cal-legend-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent3);display:inline-block;}
</style>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.23.0/firebase-app-compat.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.23.0/firebase-database-compat.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="focus-banner" id="focusBanner" style="display:none">
  <span>🎯 FOCUS — <span id="focusTask">집중 중</span></span>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px">
    <span class="focus-timer" id="focusTimer">25:00</span>
    <button class="btn btn-sm" style="background:#000;color:var(--accent)" onclick="stopFocus()">STOP</button>
  </div>
</div>

<nav>
  <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('brain')">01 Brain Dump</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab('big3')">02 Big 3</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab('backlog')">03 Backlog</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab('timebox')">04 Time Boxing</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab('review')">05 Review</div>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-left:auto;border-left:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 24px">
    <span id="syncStatus" style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--muted)">연결 중...</span>
    <div class="logo" style="border-left:none;padding:14px 0;margin-left:0">EXEC//SYS</div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- LOADING OVERLAY -->
<div id="loadingOverlay" style="position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:16px">
  <div style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:48px;letter-spacing:6px;color:var(--accent)">EXEC//SYS</div>
  <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--muted)">Firebase 연결 중...</div>
  <div style="width:200px;height:2px;background:var(--surface2);margin-top:8px"><div id="loadingBar" style="height:100%;background:var(--accent);width:0%;transition:width .4s ease"></div></div>
</div>

<!-- DATE BAR -->
<div class="date-bar" id="dateBar">
  <button class="date-nav-btn" onclick="shiftDate(-1)">←</button>
  <div style="position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;">
    <button class="date-display" id="dateDisplay" onclick="toggleCal()"></button>
    <div id="calPopup">
      <div class="cal-header">
        <button class="cal-nav" onclick="calShiftMonth(-1)">◀</button>
        <div class="cal-month-label" id="calMonthLabel"></div>
        <button class="cal-nav" onclick="calShiftMonth(1)">▶</button>
      </div>
      <div class="cal-grid" id="calGrid"></div>
      <div class="cal-footer">
        <button class="cal-today-btn" onclick="goToday()">● 오늘</button>
        <div class="cal-legend"><span class="cal-legend-dot"></span> 데이터 있음</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="date-nav-btn" onclick="shiftDate(1)">→</button>
</div>
<div class="not-today-banner" id="notTodayBanner"></div>

<!-- 01 BRAIN DUMP -->
<div class="page active" id="page-brain">
  <div class="page-title">BRAIN<br>DUMP</div>
  <div class="page-sub">머릿속을 비워라 — 판단 없이 전부 쏟아내라</div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>① 지금 머릿속에 있는 모든 것</h3>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:1px">걱정, 할 일, 아이디어 — 한 줄에 하나씩, 판단 없이</p>
    <textarea class="brain-dump" id="dumpInput" placeholder="예:&#10;다큐 촬영 시작해야 함&#10;홍대 배달 스케줄 확인&#10;카메라 배터리 충전&#10;언젠가 제주도 여행 가고 싶음&#10;유튜브 채널 만들어볼까?"></textarea>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:12px">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="processDump()">PROCESS →</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="clearDump()">CLEAR</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="dumpList" style="display:none">
    <hr class="divider">
    <div class="header-row">
      <div>
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:6px">② 각 항목을 분류하라 — <span id="dumpCount">0</span>개 남음</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px">→ BIG 3: 오늘 반드시 &nbsp;|&nbsp; → 나중에 / 언젠가: Backlog 보관 &nbsp;|&nbsp; ✕: 잡음 제거</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="dumpItems"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 02 BIG 3 -->
<div class="page" id="page-big3">
  <div class="page-title">BIG<br>THREE</div>
  <div class="page-sub">오늘 반드시 달성할 3가지 — 서브태스크로 쪼개야 실행된다</div>
  <div id="big3Container"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>새 목표 추가</h3>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px">
      <input type="text" id="big3Input" placeholder="오늘의 핵심 목표 (뭉뚱그려도 됨 — 아래서 쪼개세요)" style="flex:1">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="addBig3()">ADD</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="divider">
  <div class="grid3">
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num" id="s-done">0</div><div class="stat-label">Completed Today</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num" id="s-rate">0%</div><div class="stat-label">Completion Rate</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num" id="s-streak">0</div><div class="stat-label">Day Streak</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 03 BACKLOG -->
<div class="page" id="page-backlog">
  <div class="page-title">BACK<br>LOG</div>
  <div class="page-sub">Big 3가 아닌 것들 — 잃어버리지 않되, 지금 신경 쓰지 않는다</div>
  <div class="header-row">
    <div class="filter-row" style="margin-bottom:0">
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterBacklog('all',this)">전체</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterBacklog('later',this)">나중에</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterBacklog('someday',this)">언젠가</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterBacklog('idea',this)">아이디어</button>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" onclick="openAddBacklog()">+ ADD</button>
  </div>
  <div id="backlogList"></div>
</div>

<!-- 04 TIME BOXING -->
<div class="page" id="page-timebox">
  <div class="page-title">TIME<br>BOXING</div>
  <div class="page-sub">시간을 소유하라 — 반응하지 말고 설계하라</div>
  <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <div>
